Misty's Mini projects #1 - CLOVIS with coax 20mm ballistic

Hey guys
My 15th usersight is now up. It's a mini side project for a friend of mine who requested to make a default short range sight with the 20mm ballistic ranges for the CLOVIS. There is a readme file in the .zip for a more detailed installation guide.

Nothing too big and too special for now, just taking a bit of a break. Expect more larger projects to come.

And also credit to @Front_Wind for the thumbnail inspiration lol

This sight is only usable for the German and French CLOVIS.
